Spring Data JPA style means writing very minimal code to interact with the database by using ready-made repository interfaces provided by Spring. You donâ€™t need to write SQL or manage connections, transactions, or sessions manually.

âœ¨ Itâ€™s all about:
Less code âœ…

More readability âœ…

